# 💻 Coding Problem 1

## Reverse a Number

Input:
1234

Output:
4321

---

## Logic

```python id="mxtt81"
n = 1234
rev = 0

while n > 0:
    digit = n % 10
    rev = rev * 10 + digit
    n = n // 10

print(rev)
```

